Package: pppgram
Type: Package
Title: Periodograms for Spatial Point Patterns
Version: 0.6
Author: Tuomas Rajala
Maintainer: Tuomas Rajala <tuomas.rajala@iki.fi>
Description: Computation of (de-biased) periodograms, multitapered periodograms and isotropic periodograms for spatial point patterns. This early version supports data in spatstat::ppp-objects with rectangular data windows.
